title: Court Martial - Hassel Sven
description: Porta, Tiny, Barcelona and The Legionnaire fight a hellish war on the Finnish front... Fighting a hellish war on the Finnish front - a war of ice, blood, cold and wolves. A war where it didn't matter who won. All that mattered was to survive. But even survival could be dangerous in an army where the Fuhrer's fanatics were rife. To survive the Russian tanks, the machine guns, the flame-throwers could mean shipment to the infamous and brutal Torgau Prison where conditions were almost more savage than the Front. Survival could mean arrest, court martial and a cold grey day facing the execution squad.
